## Validation Scenario Matrix

| Scenario | What happens | Session created? | Redirect? |
|----------|-------------|------------------|-----------|
| `GET /login` | Renders `login.html` (no error) | ❌ | ❌ |
| Correct email + password | Session set, redirect to `/` | ✅ | → `/` |
| Demo user (`demo@spendly.com` / `demo123`) | Session set, redirect to `/` | ✅ | → `/` |
| Case-variant email (`Demo@Spendly.com` / `demo123`) | Normalised to `demo@spendly.com`, matches → session set | ✅ | → `/` |
| Email exists, wrong password | Error: "Invalid email or password." | ❌ | ❌ |
| Email not in DB | Error: "Invalid email or password." (same msg) | ❌ | ❌ |
| Failed login — email preserved? | ✅ email shown in input | ❌ | ❌ |
| `GET /logout` (while logged in) | Session cleared, redirect to `/login` | Cleared | → `/login` |
| `GET /logout` (while not logged in) | Session cleared (no-op), redirect to `/login` | N/A | → `/login` |

